        "title": "Arc browser’s new AI-powered features combine OpenAI and Anthropic’s models",
        "image": "https://techcrunch.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.16.25-PM.jpg?w=430&h=230&crop=1",
        "category": "Apps",
